    "title": "BPC-157: The Gastric Protective Peptide with Systemic Healing Properties",
    "executive_summary": "BPC-157 (Body Protection Compound-157) is a synthetic peptide derived from a protective protein found in human gastric juice. This 15-amino-acid sequence has demonstrated remarkable tissue repair and anti-inflammatory properties across multiple organ systems, with particular efficacy in gastrointestinal healing, making it a compelling option for conditions like SIBO, leaky gut, and inflammatory bowel disorders.",

